sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Director
    participant Hero
    participant TextParty
    participant ScrollTrigger
    participant AnimationBus
    participant LandingSeq as LandingSequence

    Note over Director: DOMContentLoaded

    Director->>+Hero: constructor(bus, smoother)
    Hero->>Hero: Find #main-header h1
    Hero->>Hero: createIntro()
    Hero->>+TextParty: roll(titleElement, settings)
    Note over TextParty: Character-by-character<br/>roll animation
    TextParty-->>-Hero: rollTimeline
    Hero->>Hero: Store rollTimeline
    Hero->>Hero: createScrollTriggers()
    Hero->>Hero: Build reverseTimeline
    Hero->>+ScrollTrigger: create(trigger, animation)
    Note over ScrollTrigger: Links scroll position<br/>to reverse animation
    ScrollTrigger-->>-Hero: ScrollTrigger instance
    Hero-->>-Director: Hero initialized

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
    Note over TextParty: Intro Animation Plays
    TextParty->>AnimationBus: onTextPartyComplete event
    AnimationBus->>LandingSeq: Notify sequence
    Note over Hero: TextParty roll complete
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over Hero: User Scrolls Down
    ScrollTrigger->>AnimationBus: emit('section:main-header:scroll:enter')
    ScrollTrigger->>Hero: Trigger reverse animation
    Note over Hero: Characters reverse out
    ScrollTrigger->>AnimationBus: emit('section:main-header:scroll:exit')
    ScrollTrigger->>AnimationBus: emit('section:main-header:outro:start')
    AnimationBus->>LandingSeq: Coordinate next section
    end
